noteLab.util.geom.unit
Class MValue

java.lang.Object
  noteLab.util.geom.unit.MValue
All Implemented Interfaces:
CopyReady<MValue>
public class MValue
extends java.lang.Object
implements CopyReady<MValue>

This class encapsulates a value along with a unit. As such, it makes the value of a number precise because it also carries along its unit. Moreover, given an object of this type, it is possible to get its value converted to any unit.

Author:
Dominic Kramer
